sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client<br/>(endpoint)
    participant D as DHCP Server<br/>(gateway)
    participant T as TFTP Server<br/>(gateway)
    participant N as NFS / HTTP Server<br/>(deployment server)

    C->>D: DHCPDISCOVER (PXE option 60)
    D-->>C: DHCPOFFER (IP, next-server, filename)
    C->>D: DHCPREQUEST
    D-->>C: DHCPACK (lease confirmed)

    C->>T: TFTP RRQ — grubx64.efi
    T-->>C: grubx64.efi (GRUB EFI binary)

    C->>T: TFTP RRQ — grub.cfg
    T-->>C: grub.cfg (boot menu)

    C->>T: TFTP RRQ — vmlinuz + initrd.img
    T-->>C: kernel + initrd

    Note over C: Kernel boots in RAM<br/>mounts root over NFS / HTTP

    C->>N: Mount deployment root (NFS or HTTP)
    N-->>C: Clonezilla live environment

    Note over C: Clonezilla starts<br/>restores AUCOOP image<br/>to local disk
